---
const email = 'contact@agentskillforge.com';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>agentskillforge.com - Practical agentic workflow agents</title>
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="agentskillforge.com helps small businesses turn agentic AI into practical, long-running workflow agents teams can shape to business goals (with training)."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-slate-200 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur">
			<div class="container flex h-16 items-center justify-between">
				<a href="#top" class="font-semibold tracking-tight">
					agentskillforge.com
				</a>
				<nav class="hidden items-center gap-6 text-sm md:flex">
					<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900" href="#services">Services</a>
					<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900" href="#different">What’s different</a>
					<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900" href="#faq">FAQ</a>
					<a
						class="rounded-lg bg-slate-900 px-4 py-2 text-white hover:bg-slate-800"
						href="#contact">Contact</a>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</header>

		<main id="top">
			<section class="container py-16 md:py-20">
				<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
					<div>
						<h1 class="text-balance text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-5xl">
							Agentic AI for <span class="text-slate-700">real workflows</span>
						</h1>
						<p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
							We help small businesses turn agentic AI into practical, long-running workflow agents that teams can shape to business goals (with training), not one-off bespoke automation.
						</p>

						<div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
							<a
								href="#services"
								class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50">Explore services</a>
							<a
								href="#contact"
								class="rounded-lg bg-slate-900 px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-slate-800">Get in touch</a>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-slate-600">
							<span class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1">Training included</span>
							<span class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1">Staff enablement</span>
							<span class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1">Long-running agents</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white p-6">
						<h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Quick overview</h2>
						<ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
								<span><strong>Trainable + shapeable</strong> agents guided toward your business objectives and operating style.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
								<span><strong>Long-running learning agents</strong> built for ongoing work, not one-off automations.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<span class="mt-0.5 inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-slate-900"></span>
								<span><strong>Staff enablement</strong> so your team can use and govern agents safely.</span>
							</li>
						</ul>

						<div class="mt-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
							<p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">Best for</p>
							<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700">
								Small businesses and their staff who want a practical agentic AI pilot without needing an in-house AI engineering team.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="different" class="border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
				<div class="container py-14">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What makes us different</h2>
					<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-slate-700">
						More than a script or a one-time integration. We build long-running workflow agents your team can shape, learn, and operate.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
						{[
							{ title: 'Long-running learning agents', body: 'Designed for ongoing work and continuous improvement.' },
							{ title: 'Trainable + shapeable', body: 'Guided toward business objectives and your operating style.' },
							{ title: 'Staff enablement', body: 'Education, governance, and rollout support for teams.' },
						].map((c) => (
								<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6" key={c.title}>
									<h3 class="text-base font-semibold">{c.title}</h3>
									<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">{c.body}</p>
								</div>
						))}
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="services" class="container py-14">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What we offer (starting menu)</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-slate-700">
					Pick a starting point and evolve from there.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
					{[
						{
							title: 'Consulting',
							body: 'Educate leaders and teams on what agents are, what to automate first, and how to design for outcomes.',
						},
						{
							title: 'Ready-made agentic systems',
							body: 'Packaged, configurable agents for common business workflows.',
						},
						{
							title: 'Pre-trained agents',
							body: 'Starting points tailored to a business’s domain and constraints.',
						},
						{
							title: 'Staff agents / training',
							body: 'Making agentic tools available to staff safely and effectively.',
						},
					].map((s) => (
						<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6" key={s.title}>
							<h3 class="text-base font-semibold">{s.title}</h3>
							<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">{s.body}</p>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="faq" class="border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
				<div class="container py-14">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
					<div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
						<details class="group rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-4">
							<summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium">What do you mean by “long-running workflow agents”?</summary>
							<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
								Agents that stay useful over time, supporting ongoing work (and learning) instead of just running once like a script.
							</p>
						</details>
						<details class="group rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-4">
							<summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium">How is this different from one-off automation?</summary>
							<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
								We design for outcomes and operating style, then help teams learn, govern, and evolve the system.
							</p>
						</details>
						<details class="group rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-4">
							<summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium">What should we automate first?</summary>
							<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
								We start with workflows that benefit from repetition, structure, and clear business goals. Then we scope, train, and ship a pilot.
							</p>
						</details>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="contact" class="container py-14">
				<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
					<div>
						<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Let’s build your first agentic workflow pilot</h2>
						<p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">
							Email us and we’ll suggest a smart starting point based on your goals and constraints.
						</p>
						<div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
							<a
								href={`mailto:${email}?subject=${encodeURIComponent('Agentskillforge - Website Inquiry')}`}
								class="rounded-lg bg-slate-900 px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-slate-800">Email {email}</a>
							<a href="#services" class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50">See services again</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
						<p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">What to include in your message</p>
						<ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
							<li>Which workflow(s) you want to improve</li>
							<li>What “success” looks like for your team</li>
							<li>Any constraints (tools, data, compliance)</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<footer class="border-t border-slate-200">
			<div class="container py-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
				<p class="text-sm text-slate-600">© {year} agentskillforge.com</p>
				<div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
					<a class="text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900" href="#top">Back to top</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
